Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切开始于神木
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断战斗\N不断祈求  不断寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从中产生了强烈的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全新的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明的未来从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得凶暴的七宝到处作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最强的敌人竟然就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉对七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法避免的宿命决斗即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导我们的最后一块碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枯井的另一边\N战国的世界里还有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战国时代的传说故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:44.15,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:53.20,OP,,0,0,0,,为谁而流的眼泪祈祷般地流下脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:02:00.40,OP,,0,0,0,,不要隐藏脆弱 温柔地接受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:08.07,OP,,0,0,0,,连呼吸都忘记 眼中的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:15.07,OP,,0,0,0,,唯有太阳闪耀着不断寻找着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:22.30,OP,,0,0,0,,凝视镜子 你一定能看见立誓的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:29.60,OP,,0,0,0,,自己的背后也有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:35.47,OP,,0,0,0,,你的改变 将改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:38.85,OP,,0,0,0,,实现梦想的爱的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:46.07,OP,,0,0,0,,穿越虚幻的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:50.20,OP,,0,0,0,,天空有光 大地有水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:59.85,OP,,0,0,0,,坚强的心灵带你到未来的 ANGELUS（奉告祈祷）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:07.12,OP,,0,0,0,,双手握紧热情的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:44.15,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在追寻宿敌奈落的旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来到彼世与此世的交界处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金钢枪破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落要把最后的\N四魂之玉碎片夺走的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后总算被成功阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  奈落接下来\N为了夺走桔梗的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出了橱子鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要用此引诱出桔梗\N并且杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为好不容易\N把桔梗这家伙给引出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔寄之树被腐蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把橱柜给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算会死也要保护橱柜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你快醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们总算\N设法解决了橱子鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是眼看着琥珀\N又成为奈落的帮凶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚的痛苦也越来越深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会后悔保护琥珀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  要是不保护他的话\N我一定会更后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的人心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑劣的奈落\N躲在幕后不露面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是就在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们遭遇到一件\N与奈落有着重大关系的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个家伙\N胆敢妨碍本大爷的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第164话\N最强的敌人  被宿蛹控制的七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝这样不是很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是吗  我很可怜耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是这次发疯暴走的\N是狐妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说狐妖是不会\N坐视小狐狸被欺负不管因而现身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这是犬夜叉的诱敌计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是还是觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个办法有点太天真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下来\N你到底把我当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正还是先把七宝放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐神大人来了\N请镇住他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  现身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来救小狐狸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是它好像是要吃七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这种杂碎妖怪\N我两三下就可以劈了它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劈了他?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是拜托你\N压制住他就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉你先退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙一定是狐神没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被什么东西附了身的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭气弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对鼻子很灵的妖怪应该会有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像对犬夜叉也起了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么狐神大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了\N邪气已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来应该会回神社去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了感谢你们\N我们准备好了饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位到我们村长家休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你们的同伴\N似乎也很痛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今晚我们就借宿打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝\N你这小子不要慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我要把你给搞哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位狐神大人守护着这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直供奉着他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无论如何都不能杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  请各位慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是有这个权力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够吃到这顿饭\N也是多亏了七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  我的份也给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一想还是不太放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个附身的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你知道那个妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是叫作“宿蛹”的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不是很厉害的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总是寄居在\N体型庞大的妖怪体内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没听说过\N会附身于土地神身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调查看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在追踪奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是跟这种杂碎妖怪\N扯上关系的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一点奈落的线索\N我就坐立难安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性急坐不住\N不一直就是你的老毛病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是因为今天没有出到风头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才一肚子不满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摆出一副什么都懂的蠢样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是七宝这小子不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对…要把你搞哭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风还真大耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿蛹?难道还有别的宿蛹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要突然\N站在别人后面说话啦  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么害怕的话\N就给我乖乖躺下来睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不只一只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你也醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到处都找不到七宝耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝刚刚挨了我一拳\N应该还躺在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的臭气弹  什么时候被他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宿蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像七宝这样的小妖怪\N要是被宿蛹附身的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母  追上七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝会像白天的土地神一样\N变得那么凶暴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为七宝\N已经输给宿蛹的邪气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要把你搞哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为臭气弹的威力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个负责去找七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐神大人终于平静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就可以安心地干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是被很大的东西给弄出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被…被暗算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁?谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黏鸟胶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师他们\N到现在都还没回来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有新的妖怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我们除掉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的妖怪\N既然不是神仙就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有枪也带着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…糟了\N再不快点找到七宝的话就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民们都快气炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的\N我的头才是快要爆炸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要抢在大家的前面\N先找到七宝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子好像已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他逃了\N快拿枪射他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别着急  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是替身球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子他根本不打算\N乖乖束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们一定要\N抢在村民之前找到他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然被你给看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  快点给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要帮你\N把背后的宿蛹拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火这点小把戏\N对我除了觉得热以外根本不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接锤球之后是呼唤陀螺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的狐妖术\N早就已经都被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有绝招没有使出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙\N有本事就尽管使出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真是倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝那小子\N比想象中还要难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  七宝好像又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不能真的下狠招教训他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还跟他客气什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要揍他五  六十下\N让他清醒清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要他清醒\N不至于要打他五六十下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这么暴力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你拿那些丸子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里头下了迷药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就比我还要阴险嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药起作用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要逮住你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你要杀了同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你以为你是小鬼\N我就会对你手下留情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝是被宿蛹附身了\N才会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛  就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还敢说“就是嘛  就是嘛”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你反应得太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是还记得自己\N刚才被附身的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才老是对我用一些怪招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为你\N一次又一次的欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说嘛\N你这小子果然都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶快去追逃走的宿蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是在寻找新的寄生体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放过它的话\N又会有人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来应该寄生在\N庞大妖怪体内的宿蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这么大规模的出现  就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们原来的寄生体\N可能已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之\N我们只能先把这里收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:21:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宿蛹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近经常看到宿蛹出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿蛹已经被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还有什么不放心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那些宿蛹的数量来看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只死掉的寄生体\N应该是很大的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然寄生体死亡\N是很理所当然的事  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们却没有看见\N那个大妖怪的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有气味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果寄生体没有死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿蛹无法再附身于寄生体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  难道你认为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事情跟奈落有关
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事情并不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错  这件事太可疑了
